{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 66,
  "title": "第六十六章（後己）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "江海所以能為百谷王者，以其善下之，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故能為百谷王。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人欲上民，"
    },
    {
      "text": "必以言下之；"
    },
    {
      "text": "欲先民，"
    },
    {
      "text": "必以身後之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人處上而民不重，"
    },
    {
      "text": "處前而民不害。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以天下樂推而不厭。"
    },
    {
      "text": "以其不爭，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故天下莫能與之爭。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "江海以卑，故眾流歸之，若民歸就王。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以卑下，故能為百谷王也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲在民之上也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "法江海處謙虛。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "欲在民之前也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先人而後己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人在民上為主，不以尊貴虐下，故民戴而不為重。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人在民前，不以光明蔽後，民親之若父母，無有欲害之心也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人恩深愛厚，視民如赤子，故天下樂推進以為主，無有厭也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下無厭聖人時，是由聖人不與人爭先後也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人皆有為，無有與吾爭無為。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
